{"tid":1291724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁定邦：市民可匿名供料監警會　不想任何人有法律風險","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:31:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b71ebdb75b5fcf84c181642da21a1d7dfd380b","tid":1291724,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190707/s00001/ea0ad611b2aead9f20ccaf00ded521cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190707%2Fs00001%2Fea0ad611b2aead9f20ccaf00ded521cb.jpg&h=f862aa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議觸發多場示威衝突，監警會早前表示將成立專責小組，主動審視與修例有關的大型公眾活動，並撰寫報告，時間範圍涵蓋6月9日至7月2日。監警會主席梁定邦接受無綫節目「講清講楚」訪問時表示，今日（7日）舉行的九龍大遊行一旦爆發衝突，將建議監警會一併審視，稱不會影響特首林鄭月娥定明完成報告的半年期限。<br />\n<br />\n梁定邦表示，現時已接獲100多條市民主動提供的片段，過去他們也錄影了多家網媒及傳媒的現場直播片段，均會用作重組事件詳情。他說，不希望任何向監警會提供資料的市民承受法律風險，故建議市民如打算向他們提供資料，可利用第三者身分，甚至是不列姓名等。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，曾打算邀請退休法官加入專責小組來提高公信力，但認為監警會成員已有數名資深大律師，加入一名法官影響不大；再加上不知未來政府會否成立獨立調查委員會，故為避免與政府爭奪任命法官而作罷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有坊間聲音質疑監警會難以跟進身上無編號的「速龍小隊」成員行為，梁定邦指出，並非所有小隊成員身上均無編號，且警方也會有小隊所有成員的資料，可以靠「抽絲剝繭」方法找出涉事成員。不過他承認，並非所有涉事成員都能使用上述方法處理。"},{"pid":"c2d57ee4f02b037178d0e94f3edaf51e1c827df1","tid":1291724,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190707/s00001/1562472342291/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190707%2Fs00001%2F1562472342291%2F&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=4337d69e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190707%2Fs00001%2F1562472342291%2F&h=995c5d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190707/s00001/1562472342291/</a>"},{"pid":"29b7a113b2914bae4a5d5e68442e37c1711a4396","tid":1291724,"uid":103230,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦冇人信監警會<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會呀⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2022e936c79b45fc965f4318e847345568f985a","tid":1291724,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee000f555c8f682d36a7f136e2ffe585524d2d06","tid":1291724,"uid":26283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:37:41.000Z","msg":"匿名咪當無收過<br />\n夠膽你咪開名企出來追<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e949c7acab4e4218a4b7e7b1d7c26e2281b6d630","tid":1291724,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"收皮啦監警會, 監你老母"},{"pid":"e533841bde77360aba8cb4d8da07b80fe63c5d0f","tid":1291724,"uid":275531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔係到今時今日仲信監警會有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8e0db4569a04e92cc25e4a4677e8e1c46b9863","tid":1291724,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"一齊去廉署舉報黑警公職人員行為失當罪<br />\n要逐個number銼死佢地"}]}